.SH NAME
cSignal  - send signal to one waiting thread.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.Ss
#include <util/ulocks.h>
.Se
.Ss
NEOERR *cSignal(pthread_cond_t *cond);

.Se

.SH ARGUMENTS
cond - condition variable to send signal on.

.SH DESCRIPTION
Sends a signal to one thread waiting on condition
variable <cond>.

